ous discussions on Facebook and web forums, a major strike is expected on 5th August (next Monday), with large scale assembly is also expected in our area. I am worried for both public safety and public transportation logistics for the day. <br />\n<br />\nAccording to OCCUPATIONAL SAFETY AND HEALTH ORDINANCE, CHAPTER 509, Employers should contribute to safety and health in their workplaces by: <br />\n* providing and maintaining safe access to and egress from the workplaces; and <br />\n* providing and maintaining a safe and healthy work environment <br />\n<br />\nMay I seek a clarification on management&rsquo;s plan?<br />\n<br />\nWill there be any disciplinary action if the employee decided to join the strike on 5 August 2019?<br />\n<br />\nWe appreciate your response by 8PM today (2 August 2019).<br />\n<br />\nNews- HK protesters call for citywide strike on August 5<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.asiatimes.com/2019/07/article/hk-protesters-call-for-citywide-strike-on-august-5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.asiatimes.com%2F2019%2F07%2Farticle%2Fhk-protesters-call-for-citywide-strike-on-august-5&d=7fFLqiM2ByXH61viL1oyjGa%2FpyP0knsd4enDGc0qzPM%3D&h=f3f052dd\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.asiatimes.com/2019/07/article/hk-protesters-call-for-citywide-strike-on-august-5</a>"},{"pid":"c24c49808560631eb58cc7462a61c314dc4c8155","tid":1396641,"uid":119984,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"139ac2de89823b8250b0091877c716a13fd38c4f","tid":1396641,"uid":42751,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"quote":{"pid":"d73a070e960ccd3d019de9e2d4d5034a8e1f7a1a","tid":1396641,"uid":244332,"like":180,"dislike":1,"score":179,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T07:21:36.000Z","msg":"你用屎眼睇野？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n篇野暗示叫人罷工喎"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T07:24:33.000Z","msg":"咪就係"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T07:27:57.000Z","msg":"睇完標題我都以為自己理解錯封email<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown